data.description: Stunningly updated end unit with attached garage! This ground floor entry home features luxury vinyl plank flooring and tile throughout. Stainless steel appliances, stylish modern fixtures, solid surface counter tops and stunning tile floor in primary bedroom. The value of updates to this home would not be attainable at this price considering the comparable sales of non-updated units in this community, plus this unit has a garage! Live a life of luxury and convenience in the gated community Villa Medici. Centrally located with convenient access to St Johns Town Center.  The amenities include a resort-style pool, grills, dog park, gated access, game Room, and a Fitness Center. The clubhouse has also been recently renovated by certified interior design experts that brought all the comforts of home to each resident and guests that visits. There is no placed quite like Villa Medici Condominiums.
